            <item><name>Gabriel Bodard</name> (<date value="2006-02-15">2006-02-15</date>): we should also note that marks of abbreviation can be tagged using <tag>orig</tag> inside the <tag>abbr</tag>...</item>
            <item><persName>Tom Elliott</persName> (<date value="2006-02-23">23 February 2006</date>): what about abbreviations like <foreign lang="lat">AUGGG</foreign>?</item>
        </list>
    </div>
